𝑻𝒂𝒎𝑵𝒖𝒓𝒔𝒆𝒔, 𝒌𝒖𝒍𝒂𝒏𝒈 𝒑𝒂! 𝑲𝒂𝒔𝒚𝒂 𝒑𝒂 𝒔𝒂𝒎𝒑𝒖!

Although wala nang face-to-face booth ang FEU Nursing Society, puwede pang sumali! The membership application extends UNTIL 𝐖𝐞𝐝𝐧𝐞𝐬𝐝𝐚𝐲,at 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟏𝟕, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓, so don’t miss out! 😊💛

Click the membership application form below to sign up on your desired department para makasama ka sa pagiging 𝐒𝐎𝐋𝐈𝐃 𝐍𝐔𝐑𝐒𝐨𝐜 member this academic year!

🔗http://bit.ly/3JKoDjY 

𝑳𝒂𝒍𝒂𝒓𝒈𝒂 𝒏𝒂! 𝑺𝒂𝒌𝒂𝒚 𝒏𝒂, 𝑻𝒂𝒎𝑵𝒖𝒓𝒔𝒆𝒔!

#NurSocNgarud
#MagniningningAngNursing

Caption by Maria Angela Josephine Aggalut
Publication Material by Aliyah Cabrera
